@title GoldPriceConsumer
 @dev This contract fetches the current price of gold (XAU) in USD from Chainlink's price feed.

@notice Fetches the latest price of gold in USD.
 @return price The latest price of 1 ounce of gold in USD, scaled by 10**8.
